				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${T}_{a}$$\end{document}) for crystallization and subsequently cooled down to a specific temperature of 20 °C (detailed fabrication process can be found in the Methods section).

